for our custom asset pipeline:

you need the following tools:
node (this means that you should also have npm)
bower (npm install -g bower)
tsd (npm install -g tsd)
grunt-cli (npm install -g grunt-cli)

---

in the ui directory, run the following commands:
npm install
bower install
tsd reinstall -so
grunt prod

alternatively:
./prod.sh

---

have a good day! :)
